  .prose :global(code) {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    padding: 1px 5px;
    border-radius: var(--r-xs);
    color: var(--text);
  }
  /* UX pass — inline code is post-classified by client script:
       · [data-cmd]   → ember pill for slash commands (/oc-audit, /oc-deploy, …)
       · [data-role=…] → role-coloured pill for skill-name mentions
