     site. Works in both themes via the design tokens. */
  .prose :global(code[data-cmd]) {
    /* LHCI calibration: var(--ember) (#e05c18) on the 12% ember-mix
       pill background nets ~4.22:1 — just below AA Normal 4.5:1 for
